    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the practice of making photographs with a pinhole camera. Light-sensitive film or paper is exposed through a tiny, lensless aperture: the resulting images have very great depth of field, but lack critical sharpness.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000020881/International Center of Photography Encyclopedia of Photography (1984)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar het maken van foto's met een gaatjescamera. Lichtgevoelige film of lichtgevoelig papier wordt belicht via een minuscule opening zonder lens: de resulterende beelden hebben een zeer grote scherptediepte, maar geen specifieke scherpte.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>是指以針孔照相機拍攝照片的技術。透過微小而無鏡頭的光圈，在感光負片或相紙上進行曝光。拍攝出來的影像景深非常深，但是缺乏清晰度。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refere-se à prática de fazer fotos com uma câmera pinhole. O filme ou papel sensível à luz é exposto através de uma abertura minúscula sem lente: as imagens resultantes têm uma profundidade de campo muito grande, mas carecem de nitidez crítica. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000316/CVAA-BR</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109633/CVAA-BR Consortium (2020-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
